6,'Recumbent Cycle','CA','Hip','  http://www.exrx.net/AnimatedEx/Cardio/RecumbantCycle.gif',' Instructions Preparation Sit on seat and grasp handle bars on sides. Place feet on pedals. Select \\quick start\\ or enter program. Execution Pedal. Comments Adjust seat so knees are short of full extension. Intensity can be altered by resistance and speed (revolutions per minute). '),(2867,'Recumbent Elliptical Cross Trainer','CA','Hip','  http://www.exrx.net/AnimatedEx/Cardio/RecumbantElipticalCrossTrainer.gif',' Instructions Preparation Sit on seat'),(2868,'Recumbent Stepper','CA','Hip','  http://www.exrx.net/AnimatedEx/Cardio/RecumbantStepperDeep.gif',' Instructions Preparation Select resistance and push \\quick start\\ or enter program. Lay back on incline with hips between handle bars. Grasps handle bars on sides and place feet on pedal platforms. Push both foot levers down by extending legs to raise weight stack. Allow one foot lever to raise up by bending hip and knee of one leg. Execution Push foot lever back down while simultaneously allowing opposite foot lever to raise up'),(2869,'Recumbent Stepper Cross Trainer','CA','Hip','  http://www.exrx.net/AnimatedEx/Cardio/RecumbantCrosstrainer.gif',' Instructions Preparation Sit on seat'),(2870,'Recumbent Upright Cycle','CA','Hip','  http://www.exrx.net/AnimatedEx/Cardio/RecumbantUprightCycle.gif',' Instructions Preparation Sit on seat and grasp handle bars on sides. Place feet on pedals. Select \\quick start\\ or enter program. Execution Pedal. Comments Adjust seat so knees are short of full extension. Intensity can be altered by resistance and speed (revolutions per minute). Apperatus is between an upright and recumbant cycle. '),(2871,'Reverse Hyper-extension','LE','Gluteus Maximus','  http://www.exrx.net/AnimatedEx/GluteusMaximus/BWReverseHyperExtension.gif',' Instructions Preparation Lay torso and waist on bench and grasp handles. Feet should be above floor with legs straight. Execution Raise legs by extending hips